Overview[]

In Arcane Odyssey, players are able to choose their names as a core identity, offering a level of personalization not found in its predecessor, World of Magic. Like the previous game, players are granted the opportunity to choose both their first name and last name, enhancing the role-playing experience. Currently there is a total of 2621 first names and 923 last names available. Names cannot be changed once the character has been created (unless they purchase a name change for 200 Robux).

Press CTRL+F to search names.

Vetex has posted files containing lists of both the first and last names available in-game. (ADD FILE LINKS HERE)
